    <a href="landing-pages.html">Landing Pages</a>
    <a href="ai.html" class="active">AI Innovation</a>
    <a href="mailto:jrudnicki13@gmail.com">Get in Touch</a>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero" style="min-height: 60vh;">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="ph-label">06 / AI Innovation</div>
      <h1>AI MARKETING<br><span style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, #3B82F6, #06B6D4, #84CC16);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">COMMAND</span><br>CENTER.</h1>
      <p class="ph-sub">I built something I wish I'd always had: a single, intelligent workspace where the entire marketing operation lives, with AI as a true strategic partner, not just a writing tool.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY I BUILT IT -->
  <section class="section section--white">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="s-label">The Origin</div>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start;">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);">Why I built it.</h2>
          <p class="body-text" style="margin-top: 1rem;">I've always believed marketers should spend less time managing work and more time creating value. Most marketing teams spend enormous energy on coordination: tracking campaigns, chasing updates, moving data between tools, writing reports nobody reads, and sitting in meetings that could have been a dashboard.</p>
          <p class="body-text" style="margin-top: 1rem;">As AI continued to evolve, I challenged myself to imagine what marketing could look like if planning, reporting, collaboration, content development, and execution all lived in one intelligent workspace. So I started building it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-in delay-1">
          <div class="identity-box" style="margin-top: 0;">
            <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75;">&ldquo;I don&rsquo;t believe AI will replace marketers. I believe it will <strong>amplify marketers who know how to use it strategically.</strong> This project is my proof of concept.&rdquo;</p>
          </div>
          <p class="body-text" style="margin-top: 2rem;">At Syspro, I introduced AI-powered workflows and operational systems that improved planning, reporting, content development, campaign execution, and team productivity, contributing to $15.5M+ in marketing-sourced pipeline and $6M+ in closed-won revenue.</p>
          <p class="body-text" style="margin-top: 1rem;">The command center takes that thinking further and builds it into a permanent system.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--dark mcc-showcase-wrap" style="padding: 5rem 0 6rem; overflow: hidden; background: #060b14; position: relative;">
    <!-- animated orbs -->
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;overflow:hidden;">
      <div style="position:absolute;width:700px;height:700px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(150,178,82,.07) 0%,transparent 65%);top:-200px;right:-150px;animation:orb-drift-a 10s ease-in-out infinite;"></div>
      <div style="position:absolute;width:500px;height:500px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(59,130,246,.07) 0%,transparent 65%);bottom:-100px;left:-100px;animation:orb-drift-b 13s ease-in-out infinite;"></div>
      <div style="position:absolute;width:350px;height:350px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(6,182,212,.05) 0%,transparent 65%);top:40%;left:45%;animation:orb-drift-a 8s ease-in-out infinite reverse;"></div>
      <!-- dot grid -->
      <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.045) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:28px 28px;"></div>
      <!-- top vignette -->
      <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:120px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#060b14,transparent);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-inner" style="max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem 3rem;">
      <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;padding:.45rem 1.1rem .45rem .85rem;border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(150,178,82,.15),rgba(6,182,212,.12));border:1px solid rgba(150,178,82,.45);box-shadow:0 0 18px rgba(150,178,82,.18),0 0 40px rgba(6,182,212,.08);margin-bottom:1.75rem;">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M13 2L4.5 13.5H11L10 22L20.5 10H14L13 2Z" fill="url(#bolt-grad)" stroke="url(#bolt-grad)" stroke-width=".5" stroke-linejoin="round"/><defs><linearGradient id="bolt-grad" x1="4" y1="2" x2="21" y2="22" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><stop stop-color="#96B252"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#06b6d4"/></linearGradient></defs></svg>
        <span style="font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#96B252,#06b6d4);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">Built with Claude Code</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">One Stack.<br>Every Channel.<br><span style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, #3B82F6, #06B6D4, #84CC16);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">Zero Silos.</span></h2>
      <p class="body-intro fade-in" style="max-width: 620px; margin-bottom: 0; color: rgba(247,243,236,.65);">A fully custom marketing ops platform: campaigns, calendar, editorial, social, paid, events, and leads in one place, with an AI agent that knows all of it. Built from scratch using Claude Code.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Tab nav -->
    <div class="section-inner" style="max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem 1.25rem;">
      <div class="mcc-tabs" style="display:flex;gap:.4rem;flex-wrap:wrap;padding:.9rem 0 1rem;border-bottom:none;margin-bottom:.75rem;">
        <button class="mcc-tab-btn mcc-active" onclick="mccSwitch(this,'mcc-s-dashboard')">Dashboard</button>
        <button class="mcc-tab-btn" onclick="mccSwitch(this,'mcc-s-campaigns')">Campaign Tracker</button>
        <button class="mcc-tab-btn" onclick="mccSwitch(this,'mcc-s-calendar')">Master Calendar</button>
        <button class="mcc-tab-btn" onclick="mccSwitch(this,'mcc-s-truepro')">Live Intelligence</button>
        <button class="mcc-tab-btn" onclick="mccSwitch(this,'mcc-s-strategy')">Agentic Strategy</button>
        <button class="mcc-tab-btn" onclick="mccSwitch(this,'mcc-s-leads')">Leads</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Browser frame -->
    <div style="max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2rem;">
      <!-- floating stat badges -->
      <div style="position:relative;">
        <div style="position:absolute;top:-18px;right:0;display:flex;gap:.6rem;z-index:10;">
          <div style="background:rgba(150,178,82,.12);border:1px solid rgba(150,178,82,.35);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border-radius:8px;padding:.35rem .7rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.4rem;box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(150,178,82,.12);">
            <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="#96B252" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="1,12 5,6 8,9 11,4 15,7"/></svg>
            <span style="font-size:.55rem;font-weight:700;color:#96B252;">218 MQLs</span><span style="font-size:.45rem;color:rgba(150,178,82,.6);">this quarter</span>
          </div>
          <div style="background:rgba(6,182,212,.1);border:1px solid rgba(6,182,212,.3);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border-radius:8px;padding:.35rem .7rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.4rem;box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(6,182,212,.1);">
            <span style="width:6px;height:6px;background:#22c55e;border-radius:50%;box-shadow:0 0 5px #22c55e;animation:mcc-pulse 1.5s infinite;flex-shrink:0;"></span>
            <span style="font-size:.55rem;font-weight:700;color:#06b6d4;">Live</span><span style="font-size:.45rem;color:rgba(6,182,212,.6);">10 campaigns running</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- gradient border wrapper -->
        <div style="padding:1.5px;border-radius:13px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(150,178,82,.5) 0%,rgba(59,130,246,.4) 40%,rgba(6,182,212,.5) 100%);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.04),0 50px 120px rgba(0,0,0,.8),0 0 60px rgba(59,130,246,.15),0 0 100px rgba(6,182,212,.08);">
        <div class="mcc-frame" style="border:none;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:none;animation:none;">
        <!-- chrome bar -->
        <div class="mcc-chrome-bar">
          <span class="mcc-dot" style="background:#ff5f57"></span>
          <span class="mcc-dot" style="background:#febc2e"></span>
          <span class="mcc-dot" style="background:#28c840"></span>
          <div class="mcc-url-pill" id="mcc-url-display">mcc.internal / dashboard</div>
        </div>

        <!-- ── SCREEN: DASHBOARD ── -->
        <div class="mcc-screen" id="mcc-s-dashboard">
                    <div class="mcc-sidebar">
            <div class="mcc-logo-block">
              <div class="mcc-logo-icon"></div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-size:.62rem;font-weight:800;color:#fff;letter-spacing:.05em;line-height:1.2;">MARKETING<br><span style="color:#06b6d4;">COMMAND CENTER</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-group-label">Overview</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item mcc-nav-active"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><rect x="0" y="0" width="6.5" height="6.5" rx="1.5"/><rect x="9.5" y="0" width="6.5" height="6.5" rx="1.5"/><rect x="0" y="9.5" width="6.5" height="6.5" rx="1.5"/><rect x="9.5" y="9.5" width="6.5" height="6.5" rx="1.5"/></svg></span> Dashboard</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><rect x="0" y="9" width="3.5" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="6.25" y="5" width="3.5" height="11" rx="1"/><rect x="12.5" y="1" width="3.5" height="15" rx="1"/></svg></span> KPIs &amp; Measurement</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="1" y="3" width="14" height="12" rx="2"/><line x1="1" y1="7" x2="15" y2="7"/><line x1="5" y1="1" x2="5" y2="5"/><line x1="11" y1="1" x2="11" y2="5"/></svg></span> Master Calendar</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 1l1.8 3.6L14 5.4l-3 2.9.7 4.1L8 10.4l-3.7 2 .7-4.1-3-2.9 4.2-.8z"/></svg></span> Agentic Strategy</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-group-label">Planning</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M2 8c0-3.3 2.7-6 6-6s6 2.7 6 6-2.7 6-6 6S2 11.3 2 8zm9.5-1.5c-.4-.4-1-.4-1.4 0L8 8.6 6.9 7.5c-.4-.4-1-.4-1.4 0s-.4 1 0 1.4l1.8 1.8c.4.4 1 .4 1.4 0l2.8-2.8c.4-.4.4-1 0-1.4z"/></svg></span> Campaigns</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M14 2H2a1 1 0 00-1 1v7a1 1 0 001 1h5l2 3 2-3h3a1 1 0 001-1V3a1 1 0 00-1-1z"/></svg></span> Social Media</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M11 2L9 4 12 7l2-2-3-3zM2 10l2 4 4-2-6-2z"/><line x1="9" y1="4" x2="12" y2="7"/></svg></span> Editorial</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><polyline points="1,12 5,6 8,9 11,4 15,7"/></svg></span> Paid Placements</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="8" cy="7" r="5"/><path d="M4 13s1-2 4-2 4 2 4 2"/></svg></span> Events &amp; Webinars</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-group-label">Leads</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="8" cy="5" r="3"/><path d="M2 14c0-3.3 2.7-5 6-5s6 1.7 6 5"/></svg></span> Leads</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-group-label">Admin</div>
            <div class="mcc-nav-item"><span class="mcc-nav-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2.5"/><path d="M8 1v2M8 13v2M1 8h2M13 8h2M3.1 3.1l1.4 1.4M11.5 11.5l1.4 1.4M3.1 12.9l1.4-1.4M11.5 4.5l1.4-1.4"/></svg></span> Settings</div>
            <div style="margin-top:auto;padding-top:1rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);">
              <div style="font-size:.65rem;color:#e2e8f0;font-weight:600;">Jessica Rudnicki</div>
              <div style="display:inline-block;font-size:.45rem;background:#3b82f6;color:#fff;padding:.15rem .4rem;border-radius:3px;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-top:.2rem;">ADMIN</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mcc-main-area">
            <div class="mcc-top-bar">
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;">
                <div class="mcc-sparkle">✦</div>
                <div>
                  <div style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;">Good morning, Jessica</div>
                  <div style="font-size:.6rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);">Today's overview across all channels</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <button class="mcc-report-btn">✉ Weekly DG Report</button>
            </div>
            <!-- stat cards -->
            <div class="mcc-stat-grid">
              <div class="mcc-stat-card"><div class="mcc-stat-label" style="color:#3b82f6;">● CAMPAIGNS</div><div class="mcc-stat-num" style="color:#3b82f6;">12</div><div class="mcc-stat-sub">Active Campaigns</div><div class="mcc-stat-bar"><div style="width:47%;background:#3b82f6;"></div></div></div>
              <div class="mcc-stat-card"><div class="mcc-stat-label" style="color:#0d9488;">● SOCIAL</div><div class="mcc-stat-num" style="color:#0d9488;">9</div><div class="mcc-stat-sub">Posts Queued</div><div class="mcc-stat-bar"><div style="width:60%;background:#0d9488;"></div></div></div>
              <div class="mcc-stat-card"><div class="mcc-stat-label" style="color:#059669;">● EDITORIAL</div><div class="mcc-stat-num" style="color:#059669;">15</div><div class="mcc-stat-sub">Blogs In Pipeline</div><div class="mcc-stat-bar"><div style="width:75%;background:#059669;"></div></div></div>
              <div class="mcc-stat-card" style="border-color:#f59e0b;"><div class="mcc-stat-label" style="color:#d97706;">● PAID</div><div class="mcc-stat-num" style="color:#d97706;">8</div><div class="mcc-stat-sub">Active Placements</div><div class="mcc-stat-bar"><div style="width:42%;background:#d97706;"></div></div></div>
              <div class="mcc-stat-card"><div class="mcc-stat-label" style="color:#f59e0b;">● EVENTS</div><div class="mcc-stat-num" style="color:#f59e0b;">19</div><div class="mcc-stat-sub">Upcoming Events</div><div class="mcc-stat-bar"><div style="width:80%;background:#f59e0b;"></div></div></div>
            </div>
            <!-- campaign list -->
            <div class="mcc-panel">
              <div class="mcc-panel-header"><span style="font-weight:700;color:#1e293b;">Campaigns</span><span style="font-size:.6rem;color:#94a3b8;">10 active · 6 planning · 8 complete</span><span class="mcc-view-all">View all →</span></div>
              <div style="display:flex;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:.75rem;">
                <span class="mcc-badge mcc-badge-gray">● Planning 8</span>
                <span class="mcc-badge mcc-badge-blue">● Active 12</span>
